
                                             Write Name of 40 prose writers in Hindi language ?
                                             
                
                Here are the names of 40 prose writers in Hindi language:

    Munshi Premchand
    Mahadevi Varma
    Jaishankar Prasad
    Harivansh Rai Bachchan
    Nirala
    Bhisham Sahni
    Amritlal Nagar
    Dharamvir Bharati
    Rajendra Yadav
    Nirmal Verma
    Mridula Garg
    Uday Prakash
    Vinod Kumar Shukla
    Kamleshwar
    Shrilal Shukla
    Shri Krishna Lal
    Gyan Chaturvedi
    Krishna Sobti
    Yashpal
    Acharya Chatursen
    Shivani
    Mannu Bhandari
    Agyeya
    Namvar Singh
    Kedarnath Singh
    Kunwar Narayan
    Amrita Pritam
    Ramdhari Singh Dinkar
    Sachchidananda Hirananda Vatsyayan 'Agyeya'
    Ashok Kumar Pandey
    Gajanan Madhav Muktibodh
    Ganga Prasad Vimal
    Shyam Saran Joshi
    Raghuvir Sahay
    Giriraj Kishore
    Sharad Joshi
    Hazari Prasad Dwivedi
    Rajendra Awasthi
    Nand Kishore Acharya
    Mannu Bhandari

Note that this is not an exhaustive list, and there are many other notable prose writers in the Hindi language.
